<meta content='How barbershops can keep men healthy' itemprop='name'>
<meta content='The barbershop can be a safe haven for black men, a place for honest conversation and trust — and, as physician Joseph Ravenell suggests, a good place to bring up tough topics about health. He&#x0027;s turning the barbershop into a place to talk about medical problems that statistically affect black men more often and more seriously, like high blood pressure. It&#x0027;s a new approach to problem solving with broad applications. "What is your barbershop?" he asks. "Where is that place for you where people affected by a unique problem can meet a unique solution?"' itemprop='description'>
